n^2 \equiv 1 \pmod{2}, 3n \equiv 1 \pmod{2}.
gcd(n^2-3n-1,2)=1
n^2-3n-1 \equiv 1+1-1 \equiv 1 \pmod{2}
\therefore \forall n \in \mathbb{Z}, gcd(n^2-3n-1,2)=1.
